NYTimes releases Gizmo, an golang microservices framework
22 Dec 2015
Tags: microservices, gRPC, @nytdevs, @jprbnsn

Didier Girard
* Summary

Gizmo offers four packages to help developers quickly configure and build microservice APIs and pubsub daemons.

The New York Times developers have been adopting the Go programming language over the last three years to build
back-end services. 

